Package: fasti
Title: Analysis of Chronological Patterns from Archaeological Count Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Nicolas",
           family = "Frerebeau",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "nicolas.frerebeau@u-bordeaux-montaigne.fr",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5759-4944"))
Description: A toolkit for absolute dating and analysis of chronological
    patterns. This package includes functions for chronological modeling
    and dating of archaeological assemblages from count data.
